reviewText: BORING! Do not waste one penny on this dvd. The host seemed very inexperienced with travel and lacked camera presence. It's as though they needed a fill in and just randomly picked her out of the crowed? She definately has a very long way to go before reaching Samantha Brown level.
the hostess didn't seem that enthusiastic about the places she visited nor the food being prepared.  Feels very Set up, didn't enjoy it at all.
